# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:38
translate chinese mari12_394b1929:

    # fr "Okay, thanks, [pcname]. I'll see you when you get here."
    fr "好的，谢谢，[pcname]。等你到了再见。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:41
translate chinese mari12_e6ab44c5:

    # "I get out of bed, get ready, and go pick her up at her house. Then we drive out to the cemetery."
    "我起床，收拾好，去她家接她。然后我们开车去了墓地。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:47
translate chinese mari12b_44391b00:

    # "She doesn't talk much on the way there, or as we somberly walk between the gravestones."
    "在去墓地的路上，她没怎么说话，当我们沉痛地走在墓碑之间时也是如此。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:49
