translate chinese mari12b_8dfc6edc:

    # fr "I'm sorry. I don't mean to be sad like this. I usually don't let people see me this way."
    fr "对不起。我不是故意要这么伤心的。我平时不会让人看到我这副样子的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:51
translate chinese mari12b_8e96bf49:

    # pc "It's okay Mari. Whatever you need, I'm here for you."
    pc "没关系，玛丽。无论你需要什么，我都会陪在你身边。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:53
