    # fr "Thank you, [pcname]. I know they're not really in this place, but every time I leave here I feel like I'm losing them all over again."
    fr "谢谢你，[pcname]。我知道他们其实不在这里，但每次离开这里，我都感觉好像又把他们失去了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:158
translate chinese mari12b_cdcdfbc7:

    # "I hold her while she cries, until she takes a deep breath and asks me to take her home."
    "我抱着她，任她哭泣，直到她深吸一口气，让我带她回家。"

