    "我们给动物们喂食，还给她的马“卡什”刷毛。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:193
translate chinese mari12b_4db51a74:

    # "Then we just sit in the fresh air and drink iced tea in the early summer breeze."
    "然后我们就坐在清新的空气中，在初夏的微风里喝着冰茶。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:195
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_31:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio36.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio36.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:196
translate chinese mari12b_1858b787:

    # fr "This has been great. Spending time with you. Doing things like a couple."
    fr "今天太棒了。能和你在一起，像情侣一样做这些事。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:197
translate chinese mari12b_ffc4a85b:

    # pc "Yeah, it's been fun."
    pc "是啊，真开心。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:199
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_32:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio37.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio37.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:200
translate chinese mari12b_d7d09581:

    # fr "I'd love to do it more often."
    fr "真希望能多这样相处。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:203
translate chinese mari12b_f2e427de:

    # "Then Mari cooks up dinner. It's a mix of different vegetables sauteed together."
    "接着玛丽做了晚饭。是各种蔬菜一起翻炒的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:204
translate chinese mari12b_169a82ad:

    # "No meat, because she's vegetarian and doesn't have any at the house, but the vegetables are all fresh, and the bread is homemade as well."
    "没有肉，因为她是素食主义者，家里也没存肉，但蔬菜都很新鲜，面包也是自制的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:205
translate chinese mari12b_d574565c:

    # "It's very tasty."
    "味道非常棒。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:208
translate chinese mari12b_756b3b11:

    # "After that, we sit in her living room and watch a movie. The Disney animated Robin Hood - her favorite."
    "之后，我们坐在她的客厅里看电影。迪士尼动画版《罗宾汉》——这是她最喜欢的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:209
translate chinese mari12b_50d1a5c2:

    # "She hums along with all the songs."
    "她跟着每一首歌哼唱。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:210
translate chinese mari12b_bb444f7c:

    # pc "These are definitely going to be in my head for the next week."
    pc "接下来的一周，这些旋律肯定会在我脑海里萦绕。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:212
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_33:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio37-2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio37-2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:213
translate chinese mari12b_8da90cc3:

    # fr "Join the club!"
    fr "同感！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:216
translate chinese mari12b_af7d8e81:

    # "We take a shower together."
    "我们一起洗澡。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:217
translate chinese mari12b_fdf6b91c:

    # "I scrub her back, taking extra time to massage her shoulders."
    "我帮她搓背，还特意多花时间按摩她的肩膀。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:220
translate chinese mari12b_5e90d934:

    # "Then we go to bed."
    "然后我们上床睡觉。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:222
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_34:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio38.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio38.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:223
translate chinese mari12b_637f5924:

    # fr "We spent the entire day together, huh?"
    fr "我们整整一天都在一起，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:225
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_35:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio39.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio39.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:226
translate chinese mari12b_47dbf3dc:

    # fr "I know I was sad through some of it, but even though this is the anniversary of the worst day in my life..."
    fr "我知道其中有些时候我很伤心，但尽管今天是我人生中最糟糕那天的周年纪念日……"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:228
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_36:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio40.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio40.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:229
translate chinese mari12b_eeeeced3:

    # fr "Somehow you turned today into the best day."
    fr "不知怎的，你却把今天变成了最美好的一天。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:231
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_37:

    # voice 'voices/mari_lovesomuch2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_lovesomuch2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:232
translate chinese mari12b_546fd524:

    # fr "I love you so much."
    fr "我好爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:233
translate chinese mari12b_51fe7806:

    # pc "I love you too, Mari."
    pc "我也爱你，玛丽。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:235
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_38:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio41.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio41.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:236
translate chinese mari12b_af93bf64:

    # fr "Just one more thing to make today perfect."
    fr "只差一件事，今天就完美了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:238
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_39:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio42.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio42.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:239
translate chinese mari12b_92a46e68:

    # fr "Please, make love to me, [pcname]."
    fr "求你，和我做爱吧，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:241
translate chinese mari12b_47510abd:

    # "We kiss as I sink into her."
    "当我进入她时，我们亲吻着。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:242
translate chinese mari12b_1becc9d2:

    # "Then we move together, every part of us connected."
    "接着我们一起律动，身体的每一寸都紧密相连。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:243
translate chinese mari12b_f4010c57:

    # "It's the closest I've ever felt to her."
    "这是我感觉离她最近的一次。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:247
translate chinese mari12b_e219a86e:

    # "And when we cum together, I feel everything that she feels."
    "当我们一同高潮时，我感受到了她的一切感受。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:248
translate chinese mari12b_e721ecdf:

    # "We hold each other close as I empty myself into her."
    "我将自己倾注进她体内，我们紧紧相拥。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:251
translate chinese mari12b_743db198:

    # "Afterwards, we continue holding each other."
    "事后，我们依然相拥着。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:252
translate chinese mari12b_2a4dc283:

    # "No words are needed. We both know what the other is thinking."
    "无需言语。我们都知道对方在想什么。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:253
translate chinese mari12b_b73d7100:

    # "Our minds and hearts and bodies are all one."
    "我们的思想、心灵和身体融为一体。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:256
translate chinese mari12b_3e0dbf15:

    # "And in the comfort of each other, we fall asleep."
    "在彼此的温暖中，我们沉沉睡去。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:259
translate chinese mari12b_a10928f0:

    # "The next day, she has to go to work, so we say goodbye early."
    "第二天，她要去上班，所以我们早早道别。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:260
translate chinese mari12b_ceb21b0a:

    # "But our lips linger on each other."
    "但我们的双唇仍依依不舍地贴在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:262
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_40:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio43.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio43.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:263
translate chinese mari12b_02e21aa9:

    # fr "You know you're welcome here any time. Any night."
    fr "你知道，你随时都可以来这里。任何一个夜晚。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:265
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_41:

    # voice 'voices/mari12audio44.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari12audio44.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:266
translate chinese mari12b_7ccfda96:

    # fr "I'd spend every day with you, like yesterday, if I could."
    fr "如果可以的话，我会像昨天那样，每天都和你在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:267
translate chinese mari12b_5addd2db:

    # pc "It was pretty great. Don't worry. We'll do it again soon."
    pc "那感觉真棒。别担心，我们很快会再这样。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:269
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_42:

    # voice 'voices/mari_okay1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_okay1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:270
translate chinese mari12b_68d82844:

    # fr "Okay."
    fr "好的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:272
translate chinese mari12b_d41d8cd9_43:

    # voice 'voices/mari_loveyou1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_loveyou1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:273
translate chinese mari12b_f3511250:

    # fr "Bye, [pcname]. I love you."
    fr "再见，[pcname]。我爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:274
translate chinese mari12b_93754ce5:

    # pc "Love you too, Mari."
    pc "我也爱你，玛丽。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:279
translate chinese mari12b_a71ca6f3:

    # "I leave her farm and drive back towards home."
    "我离开她的农场，开车往家开。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:280
translate chinese mari12b_a94d9d83:

    # "I'm not quite ready to settle down yet, but when I am, I could definitely see it being with her."
    "我还没准备好安定下来，但当那一天到来时，我确信那个人会是她。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:281
translate chinese mari12b_f9b60f9c:

    # "Being with her is just so easy. It feels natural."
    "和她在一起就是那么轻松，感觉如此自然。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari12.rpy:282
translate chinese mari12b_811aa5f5:

    # "She's amazing."
    "她太棒了。"

